parameters.messageText: We start walking through corridors and more corridors.

parameters.name: Keisuke
parameters.messageText: "You'll get used to it. Look, there are the kitchens that we use on most classes."

parameters.name: PLAYER_NAME
parameters.messageText: From the corridor that we are now, I can see a beautiful kitchen with long isles, each with a counter top stove.

parameters.name: PLAYER_NAME
parameters.messageText: Everything is so clean and shiny, so different than where I used to cook at home.

parameters.name: PLAYER_NAME
parameters.messageText: All the appliances and cooking utensils are like new, and I wonder how often they change everything there.

parameters.name: PLAYER_NAME
parameters.messageText: Sudenly, I realize Keisuke is not around anymore.

parameters.name: PLAYER_NAME
parameters.messageText: I think he was so focused on showing everything at the school that he didn't notice I stopped to admire this beautiful kitchen.

parameters.name: PLAYER_NAME
parameters.messageText: I decide to enter the kitchen to see everything from a closer distance.

parameters.name: PLAYER_NAME
parameters.messageText: As I enter, I smell Italian food. I look around and on one of the corners of the kitchen, I see a...

parameters.name: PLAYER_NAME
parameters.messageText: The most beautiful Lasagna I've ever seen. No. It's the most beautiful dish I've ever seen.

parameters.name: PLAYER_NAME
parameters.messageText: I never though a italian dish could look so beautiful.

parameters.name: PLAYER_NAME
parameters.messageText: I feel a weird sensation in my pants. It's been a while since I felt aroused about anything.
